column5: Anyone knows Mariner Magnum EFI 200 HP outboard is reliable motor? From which year were these motors made, Yr.1997? I know that Mercury and Mariner motors are completely same after Yr.1995.
Before I retired in 2000 I was in Mercury's factory in Fon Du Lac many times and the large engines have been made there. Mercs and Mariners are the same excdept fot paint.
2.5 litre and yup bullet proof,they can be set-up to turn 6k plus rpm all day long.
